text.section:
Each excavator shall provide each applicable protection notification center with adequate information regarding:
The name of the individual making the notification;
The excavator's name, address, and a telephone number;
The excavation or demolition site location or locations, each of which shall not exceed two thousand (2,000) feet in length unless the excavator and operator agree to a larger area, the city or community, county and street address, including the nearest cross street;
The type and extent of excavation or demolition to be performed;
A contact name and telephone number of the person responsible for the work to be performed.
